roc-toolkit (0.4.0+dfsg-2) experimental; urgency=medium

  * Require libunwind-dev << 14
    roc-toolkit is not compatible with libunwind from llvm-toolchain,
    so let's set a max version to ensure we use the one from the
    package libunwind instead.

