roc-toolkit (0.4.0+dfsg-1) experimental; urgency=medium

  * New upstream version 0.4.0+dfsg
  * Bump SONAME to libroc0.4
  * Update symbols file
  * Add libsndfile1-dev in Build-Deps
  * Refresh Don-t-strip-symbols.patch
  * Add upstream/metadata
  * Standards-Version: 4.7.0 (no changes required)
  * Update copyright file
  * Don't install the symlink "libroc.so.0" -> "libroc.so.0.X"
      This symlink is undesirable since the soname is not "libroc.so.0"
      but "libroc.so.0.X"; and usually versions 0.X break the API.

 -- Dylan Aïssi <daissi@debian.org>  Sat, 15 Jun 2024 17:36:58 +0200

